com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message

Interface UpdateMsgComponentsIntf

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface UpdateMsgComponentsIntf
extends Serializable
    An interface that defines the contract that a Message instance should follow for cases where some of the components of it depends upon the completion of some other Message instance.
    A Resource path of the Message instance could depend upon the completion of another Message instance that it depends upon. The Serializable message body depends upon the the other Message instance getting executed completely.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Neebal Technologies
